Package: mockr
Title: Mocking in R
Version: 0.2.1.9007
Date: 2024-04-03
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kirill",
           family = "M\u00fcller",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kirill@cynkra.com")
Description: Provides a means to mock a package function, i.e.,
    temporarily substitute it for testing. Designed as a drop-in
    replacement for the now deprecated 'testthat::with_mock()' and
    'testthat::local_mock()'.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://krlmlr.github.io/mockr/,
    https://github.com/krlmlr/mockr
